| 521-TC-004 | Update does not clear populated fields | Functional | User is in Edit mode with valid data in all fields. | 1. Verify all fields contain valid values.<br>2. Click Update.<br>3. Observe field values immediately after the click. | No fields are cleared or blanked at the time of Update initiation. |
