## Observability Validation Notes

- Confirm absence of client-side error alerts when entering Edit mode or clicking Update with valid data.
- Confirm no unexpected error events are logged during Update or Cancel actions.
- Only informational or expected validation-related logs are present.

---

## Risks & Edge Considerations

- Risk that hidden Update actions remain accessible via non-visual means.
- Risk that validation logic clears fields under edge conditions.
- Possible environment-specific delays in reflecting saved data.

